Hi, I’m from frc team 1555. I have a question about getting 2020 code uploaded onto my roborio. Is there a legacy installer for previous year’s wpilib software, or would I need to update the code manually to the 2024 format since most methods are deprecated?

The answer depends on what roborio image you’re using. The wpilib version must match a supported image version.

As for whether to find a 2020 image vs updating your code to 2024, well that’s ultimately up to you and how much effort you’re willing to spend. Updating code is likely the better option, but will probably be a bit more work.
